Q-3. Write an SQL query to fetch unique values of  DEPARTMENT from EMPLOYEE table. 
Ans. 

mysql> select distinct department from emp;

+------------+
| department |
+------------+
| HR         |
| Admin      |
| NULL       |
+------------+
