Q-23. Write an SQL query to fetch the no. of EMPLOYEEs  for each department in the descending order. 
Ans. 

> select department, count(*)  as no_of_emp from emp group by department order by department desc;

+------------+-----------+
| department | no_of_emp |
+------------+-----------+
| HR         |         3 |
| Admin      |         4 |
| NULL       |         1 |
+------------+-----------+
